{"tid":2227140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普確診宣布染疫後 美東西岸「核末日軍機」升空","createTime":"2020-10-02T14:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T09:43:15.000Z","uid":294518,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6925f74983494d5b5b26d14a315ac5c0592a4558","tid":2227140,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"川普確診宣布染疫後 美東西岸「核末日軍機」升空<br />\n<br />\n美國知名軍事記者大衛．艾克斯（David Axe）在《富比世》撰文指出，川普週五確診武漢肺炎後，美國海軍的「E-6B水星」通信中繼機在美國東岸、西岸升空，該軍機有「核末日軍機」之稱，是五角大廈的「機載核戰指揮所」，帶有特殊的通信系統和機組人員，負責指揮美國海軍的俄亥俄級核彈潛艦。"},{"pid":"2fcee2197cdcf3f4d90377aacf21d35960c600d8","tid":2227140,"uid":294518,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"艾克斯表示，美國海軍共有16架「E-6B水星」通信中繼機，能在核戰當中，向俄亥俄級核彈潛艦傳遞指示，幫助艦載人員瞄準敵方城市和軍事基地，以發射「三叉戟」飛彈（Trident）或潛射彈道飛彈 （SLBM），在川普宣布確診的幾小時內，「E-6B水星」通信中繼機出現在美國東岸、西岸絕非偶然。<br />\n<br />\n美國情報從業人員蒂姆&middot;霍根（Tim Hogan）在推特公布兩架「E-6B水星」通信中繼機的飛行軌跡，軍機為免被追蹤時常關閉發報器，但若發報器開啟，是因機組人員希望被看見，霍根認為，美國國防部顯然希望中國、俄國、北韓等核武對手明白一件事，就算三軍統帥生病，美國的核武指揮系統依舊是完整的。"},{"pid":"4915c6c7640828875e209c6dabd03fc4c6db344f","tid":2227140,"uid":275160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:12:31.000Z","msg":"sir this way"},{"pid":"37b75fc7c38e6faf7c0171fd9fb8a4e6769e4bbb","tid":2227140,"uid":294518,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"五角大廈：與川普確診無關<br />\n根據《華盛頓時報》報導，美國國防部官員表示，兩架「E-6B水星」通信中繼機確實正在執勤，但此項任務是預先計畫好的，與川普總統確診武漢肺炎無關，純屬巧合。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3218nyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3218nyH.png&h=ecc2cdea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3309958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309958&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=f4ef7576\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309958&h=6f11d1f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3309958</a>"},{"pid":"b91d7aba778ccf71c8c0cb5e6a255ca265502909","tid":2227140,"uid":91725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73489cacefb8e7b432c002f8382d799c2fadfd0b","tid":2227140,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:18:23.000Z","msg":"welcome~"},{"pid":"db59252dda8e817917aa2fcd651d2b46af7aa829","tid":2227140,"uid":143499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e25561d7bcb6ed388465734757fe0d9bb8898ba","tid":2227140,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"我懷疑香港作為中國南部大門及航運中心...<br />\n可能會率先被炸..."},{"pid":"7d7f30346be8305bc68dab359a3a243c81cf53a5","tid":2227140,"uid":275887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f92a53a031296fd54f71e3e1ddd7a3b2c144a0","tid":2227140,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e25561d7bcb6ed388465734757fe0d9bb8898ba","tid":2227140,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"我懷疑香港作為中國南部大門及航運中心...<br />\n可能會率先被炸..."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"香港都任何軍事價值可言 炸理做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11d1c6675d8d548352716c14c19e14c6b82d8a7","tid":2227140,"uid":226466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2f92a53a031296fd54f71e3e1ddd7a3b2c144a0","tid":2227140,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e25561d7bcb6ed388465734757fe0d9bb8898ba","tid":2227140,"uid":110895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor